Uh.

00:07:44.030 --> 00:07:45.340 align:middle line:90%
Were you even watching?

00:07:45.340 --> 00:07:47.780 align:middle line:90%
Watching what?

00:07:47.780 --> 00:07:49.981 align:middle line:84%
The experts
explaining mindfulness.

00:07:49.981 --> 00:07:51.210 align:middle line:84%
Oh, yeah.
Yeah, yeah.

00:07:51.210 --> 00:07:52.725 align:middle line:84%
I was watching.
-Mm.

00:07:52.725 --> 00:07:53.460 align:middle line:90%
