weren't paying attention.

00:08:06.266 --> 00:08:08.120 align:middle line:90%
Uh.

00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:09.460 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, no, I did.

00:08:09.460 --> 00:08:10.360 align:middle line:90%
I was listening to it.

00:08:10.360 --> 00:08:11.660 align:middle line:10%
Yeah, but you weren't
paying attention

00:08:11.660 --> 00:08:12.630 align:middle line:10%
and that's the problem.

00:08:12.630 --> 00:08:13.540 align:middle line:10%
Wait.
Wait.

00:08:13.540 --> 00:08:14.700 align:middle line:10%
There's a problem?

00:08:14.700 --> 00:08:16.050 align:middle line:10%
Yeah, there's a problem.

00:08:16.050 --> 00:08:17.360 align:middle line:10%
You don't pay attention.

00:08:17.360 --> 00:08:18.960 align:middle line:10%
I don't even know what
you mean because I could

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:21.130 align:middle line:10%
easily do two things at a time.

00:08:21.130 --> 00:08:23.190 align:middle line:10%
Yeah, you were texting
and hearing voices,

00:08:23.190 --> 00:08:24.130 align:middle line:10%
but you weren't listening.

00:08:24.130 --> 00:08:25.350 align:middle line:10%
What's the difference?

00:08:25.350 --> 00:08:27.080 align:middle line:10%
The difference is you
were hearing voices,

00:08:27.080 --> 00:08:28.530 align:middle line:10%
but you weren't
actually listening.

00:08:28.530 --> 00:08:29.860 align:middle line:10%
It's mindless.

00:08:29.860 --> 00:08:32.679 align:middle line:84%
All right, so tell me what
they said, if you're so smart.

00:08:32.679 --> 00:08:34.490 align:middle line:84%
It's that mindfulness
means paying

00:08:34.490 --> 00:08:38.460 align:middle line:84%
attention to what is actually
happening right now, not later.

00:08:38.460 --> 00:08:40.130 align:middle line:84%
This is what you
need to work on.

00:08:40.130 --> 00:08:42.960 align:middle line:84%
So you just want
me to be more aware,

00:08:42.960 --> 00:08:46.200 align:middle line:84%
like to hear what's happened
and to pay attention

00:08:46.200 --> 00:08:48.016 align:middle line:90%
to what's happening right now.

00:08:48.016 --> 00:08:48.730 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:08:48.730 --> 00:08:49.430 align:middle line:90%
That's it.

00:08:49.430 --> 00:08:50.130 align:middle line:90%
[SIGH]

00:08:50.130 --> 00:08:50.880 align:middle line:90%
That's a start.

