Wonderfulness, ridiculousness,
with a little sprinkle

01:07:30.020 --> 01:07:30.820 align:middle line:90%
of mindfulness.

01:07:30.820 --> 01:07:33.120 align:middle line:10%
You really learned
a lot with this.

01:07:33.120 --> 01:07:36.010 align:middle line:10%
Yeah, I mean, I guess
it's not a big deal if you

01:07:36.010 --> 01:07:38.030 align:middle line:10%
pay attention like you learn.

